{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL","title":"Analytical CDS Views — Cube, Fact, and Dimension views","phase":10,"phaseName":"Analytics & Security","category":"Analytics & Security","subcategory":"Analytical CDS","language":"abap","description":"Analytical CDS Views — Cube, Fact, and Dimension views. Key topics: @Analytics.dataCategory classifies a CDS view into one of four. A #CUBE view contains measures (quantifiable key figures) and. A #DIMENSION view provides master data / attributes (e.g., date,.","sections":[{"title":"Key Learning Points","description":"<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Analytics.dataCategory classifies a CDS view into one of four</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #CUBE view contains measures (quantifiable key figures) and</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #DIMENSION view provides master data / attributes (e.g., date,</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #FACT view is a granular, transaction-level view that can feed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Aggregation.default assigns the aggregation behavior for a</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Keyword dimensions (fields used for filtering / grouping) do not</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Analytics.query: #TRUE on a view creates a consumable analytical</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Analytical CDS — Cube · Dimension · Query</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ FLOW: Data → Cube → Query ============ -->\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Analytical CDS Architecture</text>\n\n  <!-- Data Source -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"95\" width=\"920\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"119\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Data Source Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">CDS Basic / Interface Views (I_* or direct DDIC tables)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"135\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Cube -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"165\" width=\"400\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Cube View</text>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE</text>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Transactional data (facts) + measures</text>\n\n  <!-- Dimension -->\n  <rect x=\"480\" y=\"165\" width=\"480\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Dimension View</text>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION</text>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Master data / attributes for grouping &amp; filtering</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"225\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <line x1=\"720\" y1=\"225\" x2=\"720\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Analytical Projection / Query -->\n  <rect x=\"120\" y=\"255\" width=\"760\" height=\"50\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"278\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Analytical Projection / Query View</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AnalyticsDetails.query = true · Combines cube + dimensions + filters</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"305\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"330\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"120\" y=\"335\" width=\"760\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Fiori Analytical List Page / KPI Tile / Analysis for Office</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">OData V4 Analytical Service</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ KEY FIGURES vs DIMENSIONS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"395\" width=\"920\" height=\"170\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"418\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Key Figures vs Dimensions</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"425\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"425\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"438\" width=\"430\" height=\"115\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"275\" y=\"458\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Key Figures (Measures)</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"480\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'UnitCode'</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"516\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Aggregatable numeric fields:</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"534\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX, COUNT</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"550\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: TotalPrice, BookingFee, FlightPrice</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"438\" width=\"430\" height=\"115\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"725\" y=\"458\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">Dimensions (Attributes)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"480\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AnalyticsDetails.query.filter: { multiplicity: #TO_MANY }</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@ObjectModel.text.association: '_Text'</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"516\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Grouping / filtering fields:</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"534\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Drill-down, slice, dice</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"550\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: AirlineID, CountryCode, Status</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ ANNOTATIONS REFERENCE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"580\" width=\"920\" height=\"155\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Analytical CDS Annotations — Quick Reference</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"610\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"610\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"633\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE</tspan>  →  View is an analytical cube (facts + dimensions)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"653\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION</tspan>  →  View is a dimension (master data / attributes)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"673\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AnalyticsDetails.query: true</tspan>  →  Expose as query (combine cube + dim)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"693\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AnalyticsDetails.query.maxLength</tspan>  →  Max result rows for query (default: 1000)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"713\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode / @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure</tspan>  →  Unit ref</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"733\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@ObjectModel.text.association</tspan>  →  Text association for dimension (language-dependent)</text>\n</svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"@EndUserText.label: 'Agency Dimension'\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\ndefine view entity /DMO/PRAC_DIM_AGENCY\n  as select from /DMO/agency\n{\n  key agency_id as AgencyID,\n      agency_name as AgencyName,\n      street as Street,\n      city as City,\n      country as CountryCode\n}\n\n/*\n * ====================================================================\n * SOURCE CODE: Cube View\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\n@EndUserText.label: 'Travel Cube'\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\ndefine view entity /DMO/PRAC_CUBE_TRAVEL\n  as select from /DMO/travel as T\n  inner join /DMO/booking as B\n    on B.travel_id = T.travel_id\n\n  association [0..1] to /DMO/PRAC_DIM_AGENCY as _Agency\n    on _Agency.AgencyID = T.agency_id\n\n  association [0..1] to /DMO/customer as _Customer\n    on _Customer.customer_id = T.customer_id\n{\n  key T.travel_id          as TravelID,\n      T.agency_id          as AgencyID,\n      T.customer_id        as CustomerID,\n      T.begin_date         as BeginDate,\n      T.end_date           as EndDate,\n      T.overall_status     as OverallStatus,\n\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      @Aggregation.default: #SUM\n      T.booking_fee        as BookingFee,\n\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      @Aggregation.default: #SUM\n      T.total_price        as TotalPrice,\n\n      @Semantics.currencyCode: true\n      T.currency_code      as CurrencyCode,\n\n      @Aggregation.default: #COUNT\n      B.travel_id          as NumberOfBookings,\n\n      _Agency,\n      _Customer\n}\ngroup by\n  T.travel_id,\n  T.agency_id,\n  T.customer_id,\n  T.begin_date,\n  T.end_date,\n  T.overall_status,\n  T.booking_fee,\n  T.total_price,\n  T.currency_code"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Analytics.dataCategory classifies a CDS view into one of four</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #CUBE view contains measures (quantifiable key figures) and</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #DIMENSION view provides master data / attributes (e.g., date,</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>A #FACT view is a granular, transaction-level view that can feed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Aggregation.default assigns the aggregation behavior for a</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Keyword dimensions (fields used for filtering / grouping) do not</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Analytics.query: #TRUE on a view creates a consumable analytical</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Analytical CDS — Cube · Dimension · Query</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ FLOW: Data → Cube → Query ============ -->\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Analytical CDS Architecture</text>\n\n  <!-- Data Source -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"95\" width=\"920\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"119\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Data Source Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">CDS Basic / Interface Views (I_* or direct DDIC tables)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"135\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"160\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Cube -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"165\" width=\"400\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Cube View</text>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE</text>\n  <text x=\"240\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Transactional data (facts) + measures</text>\n\n  <!-- Dimension -->\n  <rect x=\"480\" y=\"165\" width=\"480\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Dimension View</text>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION</text>\n  <text x=\"720\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Master data / attributes for grouping &amp; filtering</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"225\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <line x1=\"720\" y1=\"225\" x2=\"720\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Analytical Projection / Query -->\n  <rect x=\"120\" y=\"255\" width=\"760\" height=\"50\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"278\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Analytical Projection / Query View</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AnalyticsDetails.query = true · Combines cube + dimensions + filters</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"305\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"330\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"120\" y=\"335\" width=\"760\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Fiori Analytical List Page / KPI Tile / Analysis for Office</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">OData V4 Analytical Service</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ KEY FIGURES vs DIMENSIONS ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"395\" width=\"920\" height=\"170\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"418\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Key Figures vs Dimensions</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"425\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"425\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"60\" y=\"438\" width=\"430\" height=\"115\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"275\" y=\"458\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Key Figures (Measures)</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"480\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'UnitCode'</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"516\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Aggregatable numeric fields:</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"534\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX, COUNT</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"550\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: TotalPrice, BookingFee, FlightPrice</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"438\" width=\"430\" height=\"115\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"725\" y=\"458\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">Dimensions (Attributes)</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"480\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AnalyticsDetails.query.filter: { multiplicity: #TO_MANY }</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"498\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@ObjectModel.text.association: '_Text'</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"516\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Grouping / filtering fields:</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"534\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Drill-down, slice, dice</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"550\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: AirlineID, CountryCode, Status</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ ANNOTATIONS REFERENCE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"580\" width=\"920\" height=\"155\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"603\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Analytical CDS Annotations — Quick Reference</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"610\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"610\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"633\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE</tspan>  →  View is an analytical cube (facts + dimensions)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"653\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION</tspan>  →  View is a dimension (master data / attributes)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"673\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AnalyticsDetails.query: true</tspan>  →  Expose as query (combine cube + dim)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"693\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@AnalyticsDetails.query.maxLength</tspan>  →  Max result rows for query (default: 1000)</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"713\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@Semantics.amount.currencyCode / @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure</tspan>  →  Unit ref</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"733\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\"><tspan font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">@ObjectModel.text.association</tspan>  →  Text association for dimension (language-dependent)</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@EndUserText.label: 'Agency Dimension'\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\ndefine view entity /DMO/PRAC_DIM_AGENCY\n  as select from /DMO/agency\n{\n  key agency_id as AgencyID,\n      agency_name as AgencyName,\n      street as Street,\n      city as City,\n      country as CountryCode\n}\n\n/*\n * ====================================================================\n * SOURCE CODE: Cube View\n * ====================================================================\n */\n\n@EndUserText.label: 'Travel Cube'\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\ndefine view entity /DMO/PRAC_CUBE_TRAVEL\n  as select from /DMO/travel as T\n  inner join /DMO/booking as B\n    on B.travel_id = T.travel_id\n\n  association [0..1] to /DMO/PRAC_DIM_AGENCY as _Agency\n    on _Agency.AgencyID = T.agency_id\n\n  association [0..1] to /DMO/customer as _Customer\n    on _Customer.customer_id = T.customer_id\n{\n  key T.travel_id          as TravelID,\n      T.agency_id          as AgencyID,\n      T.customer_id        as CustomerID,\n      T.begin_date         as BeginDate,\n      T.end_date           as EndDate,\n      T.overall_status     as OverallStatus,\n\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      @Aggregation.default: #SUM\n      T.booking_fee        as BookingFee,\n\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      @Aggregation.default: #SUM\n      T.total_price        as TotalPrice,\n\n      @Semantics.currencyCode: true\n      T.currency_code      as CurrencyCode,\n\n      @Aggregation.default: #COUNT\n      B.travel_id          as NumberOfBookings,\n\n      _Agency,\n      _Customer\n}\ngroup by\n  T.travel_id,\n  T.agency_id,\n  T.customer_id,\n  T.begin_date,\n  T.end_date,\n  T.overall_status,\n  T.booking_fee,\n  T.total_price,\n  T.currency_code</code></pre>","tags":["cds-views"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">analytical roles: #CUBE, #FACT, #DIMENSION, or #QUERY — each</p><p class=\"mb-2\">determines how the view is interpreted by analytical engines</p><p class=\"mb-2\">(SAP Analytics Cloud, Analysis for Office, etc.).</p><p class=\"mb-2\">dimensions (characteristics); it is the primary data source for</p><p class=\"mb-2\">analytical queries. Measures must be annotated with</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@Aggregation.default to define how they are aggregated.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">product, customer) and is associated to a cube or fact view via</p><p class=\"mb-2\">CDS associations. It contains no measures.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">into cubes. The distinction from #CUBE is subtle: a #FACT view</p><p class=\"mb-2\">typically has no pre-defined aggregations and exposes all</p><p class=\"mb-2\">transactional detail; a #CUBE is the consumable analytical layer.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">measure: #SUM, #MIN, #MAX, #COUNT, #AVG, #FORMULA (for calculated</p><p class=\"mb-2\">measures), or #NONE (for dimensions / non-aggregatable fields).</p><p class=\"mb-2\">get @Aggregation.default; they are implicitly grouped-on in SQL.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Association to dimension views is the recommended pattern for</p><p class=\"mb-2\">enriching cube data with text / attributes.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">query that can be exposed via InA / OData for reporting tools.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">In modern S/4HANA, provider contract analytical_query is the</p><p class=\"mb-2\">preferred successor (see ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL_V3).</p><p class=\"mb-2\">COMPARISON TABLE: Cube vs Fact vs Dimension vs Query</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Feature         | #CUBE            | #FACT             | #DIMENSION     | #QUERY</p><p class=\"mb-2\">----------------|------------------|-------------------|----------------|-----------------------</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Measures        | Yes              | Yes               | No             | Yes (restricted)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Aggregation     | Always defined   | Optional          | N/A            | Inherited / overridden</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Associations    | To dimensions    | To dimensions     | To other dims  | Based on cube/dim</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Consumption     | Analytics tools  | Cubes / queries   | Cubes, facts   | End-user reporting</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Text support    | Via association  | Via association   | Native         | Via association</p><p class=\"mb-2\">S/4HANA 2025+   | Supported        | Supported         | Supported      | Legacy (use V3)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Example use     | Sales cube       | Sales line items  | Product / Date | Quarterly sales report</p><p class=\"mb-2\">SOURCE CODE: Dimension View</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/analytical-cds.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"ZPRAC_CDS_ANALYTICAL","sqlViewName":"","topic":"@Analytics.dataCategory: #CUBE / #FACT / #DIMENSION"}